			  </div>
			  <div>
				<h3 class="font-Atkinson">Do I need a large garden?</h3>
				<p>No, the herbs can grow in pots or small garden patches.</p>
			  </div>
			  <div>
				<h3 class="font-Atkinson">Where do you ship?</h3>
				<p>The kit is available for shipping in the United States.</p>
			  </div>
			</div>
		  </section>
	  
		  <!-- CTA -->
		  <section class="text-center py-12 bg-green-200">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Don’t Wait – Start Growing Your Healing Garden Today</h2>
			<a href="https://medicinalseedkit.com/kit/?ref=your-affiliate-id" class="bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl transition">Order Your Kit Now</a>
		  </section>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
